    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Once the pepper has softened, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>drained king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min</p>",
